analysis of the new trial. For the new trial, data and parame
ter are denoted by X and φ for the test and by Y and ψ for
the control treatment, respectively. For ease of presentation
we will assume that no nuisance parameters are present, and
that no relevant prior information on the test parameter φ is
available.
